 *
 * native_sim has no I²S controller.  alp_i2s_open returns NULL
 * with last_error = ALP_ERR_NOT_READY; the example exits.  On
 * real silicon the alp-i2s0 alias must point at the SoC's I²S
 * node (e.g. Alif's I2S0 or Renesas's SAI/SSI).
